3 ROC Curves

scd$AXchangeInverse <- -1 * scd$AXchange
wpred <- scd[, (colnames(scd) %in% c("MRN", "FEV1pred", "FEV1FVC", "FEF2575pred", 
    "R5Hzpred", "AX", "FEV1change", "FEV1FVCchange", "FEF2575change", "R5changeInverse", 
    "AXchangeInverse", "Asthma"))]

wpred$Asthma <- as.character(wpred$Asthma)

for (i in 1:length(wpred$Asthma)) {
    if (is.na(wpred$Asthma[i]) == F & wpred$Asthma[i] == "Yes") {
        wpred$Asthma[i] = 1
    }
    if (is.na(wpred$Asthma[i]) == F & wpred$Asthma[i] == "No") {
        wpred$Asthma[i] = 0
    }
}

wpred$Asthma <- as.numeric(wpred$Asthma)

    if (is.na(wpred$Asthma[i]) == F & wpred$Asthma[i] == "No") {
        wpred$Asthma[i] = 0
    }
}

wpred$Asthma <- as.numeric(wpred$Asthma)
wpred$Asthma <- factor(wpred$Asthma)

train = sample(wpred$MRN, ceiling((dim(wpred)[1]) * 100/100))

test = wpred$MRN[!(wpred$MRN %in% train)]

    "Asthma"))])

y_train = data.matrix(wpred[wpred$MRN %in% train, c("Asthma")])

x_test = data.matrix(wpred[(wpred$MRN %in% test), !(colnames(wpred) %in% c("MRN", 
    "Asthma"))])

y_test = data.matrix(wpred[wpred$MRN %in% test, c("Asthma")])

library(h2o)

    c("MRN", "Asthma"))]))

best_seednumber = 1234
best_test_error_mean = 2
best_test_error_std = NA_real_
best_param = list()

for (iter in 1:100) {
    
    seed.number = sample.int(10000, 1)[[1]]
    set.seed(seed.number)
    
    hyper_params <- list(activation = sample(c("Tanh", "TanhWithDropout"), 1), 
        input_dropout_ratio = runif(1, 0, 0.05), l1 = sample(seq(0, 1e-04, 1e-06), 
            1), l2 = sample(seq(0, 1e-04, 1e-06), 1))
    
    h2o.dl.3 <- h2o.deeplearning(x = 1:dim(x_train.hex)[2] - 1, y = dim(x_train.hex)[2], 
        training_frame = x_train.hex, nfolds = 3, ignore_const_cols = F, seed = seed.number, 
        reproducible = T, keep_cross_validation_predictions = T, loss = "Automatic", 
        hidden = c(200, 200), fold_assignment = "Modulo", stopping_metric = "misclassification", 
        activation = hyper_params$activation, input_dropout_ratio = hyper_params$input_dropout_ratio, 
        l1 = hyper_params$l1, l2 = hyper_params$l2, missing_values_handling = "MeanImputation")
    
    min_test_error_mean = as.numeric(h2o.dl.3@model$cross_validation_metrics_summary["err", 
        "mean"])
    min_test_error_std = as.numeric(h2o.dl.3@model$cross_validation_metrics_summary["err", 
        "sd"])
    
    if (min_test_error_mean < best_test_error_mean) {
        
        best_test_error_mean = min_test_error_mean
        best_test_error_std = min_test_error_std
        best_seednumber = seed.number
        
        best_param = hyper_params
    }
}
